76561197972229966,Recommended,270850,8841519,"Posted: 25 January, 2014",all,[HvK]Caecitas,"An astoundingly relaxing title for those who enjoy a little logical problem solving wrapped up in a neat little educational package. At no point could the game be considered a replacement for a formal mechanical education, but as you progress through job after job a little common sense goes a long way, and patterns emerge as you learn to associate particular faults and issues with components. While this will not help you put together that kit-car you’ve promised yourself for 20 years, it will give you an insight into the likely causes of common problems and test your ability to narrow down the offending item.Reasonably priced, well-polished for its price point and even a little educational – a very reasonable product indeed for anyone who wants to get a feeling for the causes of common car problems, or if you just enjoy a little problem solving."
